OL,3,CPhlebotomists accept deal ending
OL,4,Clongest running strike in NHS history
OL,6,FSpecialist blood staff working for the
OL,7,FNHS in Gloucestershire have voted to
OL,8,Faccept a deal, ending the longest-
OL,9,Frunning strike in NHS history.
OL,11,FPhlebotomists at Gloucestershire Royal
OL,12,Fand Cheltenham General hospitals have
OL,13,Fbeen on strike for 350 days in the
OL,14,Fdispute over pay and job evaluations.
OL,15,FThey say their work has been
OL,16,Fundervalued for years, despite the
OL,17,Fskills and responsibilities required
OL,18,Fto take and handle blood samples.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
