PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773234702
OL,3,CPhlebotomists accept deal ending
OL,4,Clongest running strike in NHS history
OL,6,FThey'll now return to work on Monday,
OL,7,F16 March, after accepting a deal that
OL,8,Fwill see their pay and roles reviewed
OL,9,Fby an independent job evaluation panel.
OL,11,FAs part of the agreement,
OL,12,FGloucestershire Hospitals NHS
OL,13,FFoundation Trust has committed to
OL,14,Frecognising the specialist nature of
OL,15,Fthe phlebotomy role and will consult
OL,16,Fstaff on the future of the service.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
