FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773234702
OL,3,CPhlebotomists accept deal ending
OL,4,Clongest running strike in NHS history
OL,6,FPhlebotomist and UNISON steward
OL,7,FCaroline Hayhurst said: "After 350
OL,8,Fdays on strike, staff are relieved the
OL,9,Ftrust has finally recognised the need
OL,10,Fto review pay.
OL,12,F"This dispute has always been about
OL,13,Ffairness and respect for the skilled
OL,14,Fwork phlebotomists do.
OL,16,F"We're keen to get back to work, doing
OL,17,Fthe job we love and providing the
OL,18,Fhighest quality care for patients."
OL,26,@oD@YOUtD@AOUxD@AOUzD@cO]
