OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773234702
OL,3,CPhlebotomists accept deal ending
OL,4,Clongest running strike in NHS history
OL,6,FUNISON South West regional secretary
OL,7,FTim Roberts added: "Phlebotomy staff
OL,8,Fhave shown incredible determination
OL,9,Fthroughout this lengthy dispute.
OL,11,F"After nearly a year of strike action,
OL,12,Fthey're looking forward to going back
OL,13,Fto their jobs and putting their
OL,14,Fexpertise to good use."
OL,26,@oD@TOUsD@AOU
